Class CcddPy4JScriptEngineFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • CCDD.CcddPy4JScriptEngineFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javax.script.ScriptEngineFactory

    class CcddPy4JScriptEngineFactory
extends java.lang.Object
implements javax.script.ScriptEngineFactory
    CFS Command and Data Dictionary Py4J script engine factory class. This class handles script engine factory calls and allows the API to treat Py4J as a JSR-223 compliant scripting language
